An event driven long/short investment strategy
Focused on the Community and Regional Banking Sectors






We seek to provide investors with an event driven, long/short investment strategy focused on the community and regional banking sectors. We employ a fundamental, relative value approach to capitalize on the ongoing consolidation trend in the community and regional banking sectors. Our strategy is to invest in (i) banks that are acquisition targets of aggressive consolidators and capturing takeover premiums in advance of acquisition announcement and (ii) select merger arbitrage transactions post-acquisition announcement. The senior investment team has nearly 40 years of experience evaluating and investing in the sector and have worked together for almost 20 years.








