How do I update this listing?




                                             Context BH Capital Management is based out of Bala Cynwyd. Context BH Capital Management is a hedge fund  with  1-10 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $397,080,207 (Form ADV from 2017-03-30).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $259,864,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 35.87%. Context BH Capital Management's largest holding is Merchants Bancshares Inc with shares held of 293,362.   WhaleWisdom has at least 6 13Fs and  21 13D/G filings in our database for Context BH Capital Management. 
                                           














